---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../../../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  title="E-Learning in Islamic Studies | Dr. Haitham A. El-Ghareeb"
  description="A section for initiatives and ideas in digital Islamic learning"
>
  <main class="page-main page-main--detail">
    <section class="shell hero hero--detail">
      <p class="hero__eyebrow">E-Learning in Islamic Studies</p>
      <h1 class="hero__title">Islamic learning in a structured digital setting</h1>
      <p class="hero__lead">
        This section is reserved for ideas, initiatives, and materials that connect Islamic learning
        with digital delivery, pedagogical structure, and educational media.
      </p>

      <div class="hero__badge-row">
        <span class="hero__badge">Digital learning</span>
        <span class="hero__badge">Pedagogy and media</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="shell notice-card">
      <h2 class="section-title">Expected content directions</h2>
      <p>
        It can later host course-related material, educational experiments, and essays on how digital
        structure can serve the communication of Islamic knowledge.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
